  "texts": [
    "The black box problem poses significant challenges, including difficulties in debugging and trust-building among users.",
    "In educational settings, students and educators may find it difficult to trust or learn from AI-generated feedback if the reasoning underlying the responses is unclear.",
    "Similarly, in medical contexts, health care professionals need to understand the basis of AI-generated diagnoses or treatment recommendations to ensure patient safety and provide informed care.",
    "Approaches such as explainable AI (XAI) and uncertainty quantification offer promising solutions to these challenges.",
    "Explainable AI aims to make AI models more transparent by providing insights into how decisions are made, thereby enhancing trust and facilitating better decision-making."
  ],
